[Amit Varma]: One of the things I've worked on in recent years is on getting my reading habit together.

00:03:03.360 --> 00:03:08.720
[Amit Varma]: This involves making time to read books, but it also means reading long form articles and essays.

00:03:08.720 --> 00:03:13.600
[Amit Varma]: There's a world of knowledge available through the internet. But the big question we all face is,

00:03:13.600 --> 00:03:18.320
