[Amit Varma]: Every day for six months, they sent me a long form article to read. The subjects covered went

00:03:38.720 --> 00:03:44.400
[Amit Varma]: from machine learning to mythology, to mental models to even marmalade. This helped me build

00:03:44.400 --> 00:03:49.120
[Amit Varma]: a habit of reading. At the end of every day, I understood the world a little better than I had

