01:16:37.760 --> 01:16:45.680
[Guest]: to those girls so i started to think about this and i knew that i didn't want to do this as an

01:16:45.680 --> 01:16:50.480
[Guest]: essay or as a report that there's something else i'm getting at but i didn't know what

01:16:50.480 --> 01:16:56.000
[Guest]: but i had a lot of conversations in my mind like things i'd overheard dialogues bits of dialogue

01:16:56.560 --> 01:17:03.120
[Guest]: so i began by just writing that down that okay i remember this exchange uh between two people now

01:17:03.120 --> 01:17:07.840
[Guest]: what happens if i take these two dialogues and i take these two characters and i open it out

01:17:08.480 --> 01:17:14.720
