01:19:11.840 --> 01:19:17.600
[Amit Varma]: you want to watch at normal speed but the reason they did that is because the blind people they

01:19:17.600 --> 01:19:23.600
[Amit Varma]: watch netflix in a sense by listening to a visual description of what's going on and because the

01:19:23.600 --> 01:19:28.560
