01:20:06.240 --> 01:20:11.120
[Amit Varma]: is that one of course as you mentioned it gives you the freedom that you're not bound by form or

01:20:11.120 --> 01:20:16.800
[Amit Varma]: house style or theme or whatever you can go in different directions you can write one para you

