[Amit Varma]: can write 50 paras but the other thing it does is that not only do you go off in all these different

01:20:21.440 --> 01:20:26.480
[Amit Varma]: directions because you are not self-conscious because what you are writing is only a blog

01:20:26.480 --> 01:20:31.680
