01:20:31.680 --> 01:20:36.240
[Amit Varma]: active i did more than 8 000 posts i think whatever the quality of those might have been

01:20:36.240 --> 01:20:43.680
[Amit Varma]: it's only constant iteration that makes you better and therefore and my other sort of speculation

