01:21:25.600 --> 01:21:30.800
[Amit Varma]: drama and filmmaking and stories and you just did everything which i can't tell you how much i admire

01:21:30.800 --> 01:21:37.360
[Amit Varma]: because i think a lot of factors hold people back from doing that such as confidence to begin with

01:21:37.360 --> 01:21:44.560
[Amit Varma]: but did exploring all these different forms did they start changing you and the kind of

01:21:44.560 --> 01:21:49.920
[Amit Varma]: explorations you made and the kind of writer you eventually became i mean starting with blogging

